hours_text:
Volunteer carvers are at work on Wednesdays, Thursdays, and Saturdays. Each one of them has their own unique style and help our visitors better understand the wildfowl arts. When you visit the museum and Boathouse (when open), be sure to visit our carvers.

Ed Morrison

Roy Carlson

Jamie Champe

Pete Taylor

George Walker

Ben Purvis

Gentry Childress
